Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.50,0:00:18.63,001,NTP,0,0,0,,（开始）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.64,0:00:34.65,001,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂事的时候爸爸就不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.65,0:00:43.65,001,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈到晚上就会出门
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.66,0:00:48.66,001,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候好几天也不回家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.63,0:00:52.63,001,NTP,0,0,0,,每次都说都是为了你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.63,0:00:56.63,001,NTP,0,0,0,,每次都感觉她很累
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.63,0:00:59.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,我不管再饿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.64,0:01:03.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,都不会抱怨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.64,0:01:06.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,会等到妈妈给我饭吃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.65,0:01:11.65,001,NTP,0,0,0,,但忍不住就跑出去找妈妈了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.63,0:01:25.63,001,NTP,0,0,0,,（聊天）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.65,0:03:24.65,001,NTP,0,0,0,,不会死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.63,0:03:41.63,001,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.64,0:03:53.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,好饿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.63,0:04:15.63,001,NTP,0,0,0,,要吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.65,0:04:34.65,001,NTP,0,0,0,,那么饿吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:39.66,001,NTP,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.66,0:04:42.63,001,NTP,0,0,0,,从哪里来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:46.63,001,NTP,0,0,0,,几岁?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:14.66,001,NTP,0,0,0,,（讨论这个女孩儿的事）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:22.65,001,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.65,0:08:32.66,001,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道你是从哪来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.63,0:08:43.63,001,NTP,0,0,0,,我来帮你洗干净
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.64,0:08:51.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,不会烫吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.66,0:09:11.63,001,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.63,0:09:15.63,001,NTP,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.64,0:09:21.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.64,0:09:24.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.65,0:10:12.66,001,NTP,0,0,0,,帮你冲干净
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:05.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,越来越干净了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.65,0:11:17.65,001,NTP,0,0,0,,用肥皂洗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.65,0:11:20.66,001,NTP,0,0,0,,看那边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.64,0:11:35.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,有被这样洗过吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.64,0:11:39.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.65,0:11:43.65,001,NTP,0,0,0,,我来帮你洗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.65,0:11:46.65,001,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.65,0:11:51.66,001,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.64,0:12:16.65,001,NTP,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.65,0:12:20.65,001,NTP,0,0,0,,手伸直
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.64,0:12:46.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.65,0:12:58.66,001,NTP,0,0,0,,这里也要洗干净
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.63,0:13:09.63,001,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.63,0:13:12.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉得出来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.65,0:13:28.65,001,NTP,0,0,0,,有点痒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.65,0:13:31.66,001,NTP,0,0,0,,帮你弄干净
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.66,0:13:34.66,001,NTP,0,0,0,,张开点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.64,0:13:50.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,帮你弄干净
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:14:01.65,001,NTP,0,0,0,,有变干净吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.63,0:14:17.63,001,NTP,0,0,0,,有点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.64,0:14:22.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,再帮你弄干净
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:37.65,001,NTP,0,0,0,,这里不弄干净不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.63,0:14:46.63,001,NTP,0,0,0,,会痒？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.63,0:14:52.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,这里也帮你弄干净
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.63,0:15:25.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.64,0:15:28.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,张开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.65,0:15:45.66,001,NTP,0,0,0,,再帮你弄干净一点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.63,0:15:58.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.64,0:16:01.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.64,0:16:04.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,有点怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.64,0:16:07.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.65,0:16:15.65,001,NTP,0,0,0,,只是帮你弄干净而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:40.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.64,0:17:09.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.64,0:17:12.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,变得奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.64,0:17:15.65,001,NTP,0,0,0,,屁股朝这边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.65,0:17:18.65,001,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.65,0:17:20.65,001,NTP,0,0,0,,变奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.65,0:17:23.65,001,NTP,0,0,0,,我帮你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.63,0:17:34.63,001,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.63,0:17:39.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,好痒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.64,0:17:42.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,会痒？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.64,0:17:44.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.64,0:17:47.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.63,0:18:14.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,好痒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.64,0:18:18.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.64,0:18:22.65,001,NTP,0,0,0,,好像没事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.66,0:18:35.66,001,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.66,0:18:38.63,001,NTP,0,0,0,,都洗干净了还黏黏的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.63,0:18:41.63,001,NTP,0,0,0,,给我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:49.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.64,0:18:52.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,你看黏黏的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.65,0:19:04.65,001,NTP,0,0,0,,这里好湿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.66,0:19:14.63,001,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.64,0:19:24.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.64,0:19:27.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,从你里面跑出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.64,0:19:30.65,001,NTP,0,0,0,,是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.65,0:19:33.65,001,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.65,0:19:36.65,001,NTP,0,0,0,,跑出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.65,0:19:40.66,001,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.64,0:20:00.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,听得到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.65,0:20:06.65,001,NTP,0,0,0,,不停的在流
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.66,0:20:16.66,001,NTP,0,0,0,,帮你舔干净
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.63,0:20:21.63,001,NTP,0,0,0,,这是尿尿的地方很脏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.63,0:20:26.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.65,0:20:42.65,001,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.63,0:20:55.63,001,NTP,0,0,0,,会变得好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.65,0:21:27.63,001,NTP,0,0,0,,变奇怪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.63,0:21:30.63,001,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.63,0:21:33.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.64,0:21:41.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,好湿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.65,0:21:49.65,001,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.66,0:21:55.66,001,NTP,0,0,0,,换你帮我弄干净
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.63,0:22:03.63,001,NTP,0,0,0,,你是很乖的小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.64,0:22:10.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.64,0:22:14.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,弄干净
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.64,0:22:17.65,001,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么弄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.65,0:22:20.65,001,NTP,0,0,0,,学我舔干净
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.65,0:22:26.66,001,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.63,0:22:32.63,001,NTP,0,0,0,,边看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.63,0:22:33.63,001,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.63,0:22:36.63,001,NTP,0,0,0,,舔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.64,0:22:48.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,用嘴巴含住
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.65,0:22:52.65,001,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.66,0:23:02.66,001,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.63,0:23:08.63,001,NTP,0,0,0,,舔干净
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.64,0:23:23.65,001,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.65,0:23:32.66,001,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.66,0:23:35.66,001,NTP,0,0,0,,看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.63,0:23:39.63,001,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.63,0:23:42.63,001,NTP,0,0,0,,用嘴巴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.63,0:23:46.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,含到底
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.64,0:23:56.65,001,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.65,0:24:02.65,001,NTP,0,0,0,,含到底
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.63,0:24:12.63,001,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.63,0:24:14.63,001,NTP,0,0,0,,很难受
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.63,0:24:17.63,001,NTP,0,0,0,,看着我
