Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.63,0:27:08.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,舌头伸出来
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.63,0:32:40.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.64,0:32:43.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.64,0:32:47.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,醒了？
