Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.66,0:36:59.63,001,NTP,0,0,0,,别动
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.66,0:38:04.63,001,NTP,0,0,0,,这里好干净
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.63,0:38:41.63,001,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.63,0:38:43.63,001,NTP,0,0,0,,会发出声音？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.63,0:38:46.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,会痒
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.64,0:38:49.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.64,0:38:52.64,001,NTP,0,0,0,,给我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.65,0:39:02.65,001,NTP,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.65,0:39:33.65,001,NTP,0,0,0,,不许出声哦
